item.title: Wierd java error,
item.dc:creator: @relmitos relmitos
item.description:
@relmitos wrote:

Did you edit your system variables?[br][br][size=1]Posted on: November 27, 2009, 05:41:49 pm[/size][hr]Should look like this: C:\Windows\System32;C:\Windows;C:\Windows\System32\Wbem;C:\Program Files (86x)\Java\jdk1.6.0_16;.
Javaw.exe and Java.exe are stored in System32. So if you’ve removed the default variables your system won’t be able to find them.
